&lt;h2 id="operations">Operations&lt;/h2>
&lt;h3 id="schedulecircuit-schedulecircuitop">&lt;code>schedule.circuit&lt;/code> (schedule::CircuitOp)&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>&lt;em>Represents a schedulable circuit.&lt;/em>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Syntax:&lt;/p>
&lt;pre tabindex="0">&lt;code>operation ::= `schedule.circuit` attr-dict $targetClock $body
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;p>Traits: &lt;code>IsolatedFromAbove&lt;/code>, &lt;code>NoTerminator&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Interfaces: &lt;code>RegionKindInterface&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
&lt;h4 id="attributes">Attributes:&lt;/h4>
&lt;table>
&lt;tr>&lt;th>Attribute&lt;/th>&lt;th>MLIR Type&lt;/th>&lt;th>Description&lt;/th>&lt;/tr>
&lt;tr>&lt;td>&lt;code>targetClock&lt;/code>&lt;/td>&lt;td>::mlir::FloatAttr&lt;/td>&lt;td>32-bit float attribute&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>
&lt;/table>
&lt;h3 id="scheduleoperation-scheduleoperationop">&lt;code>schedule.operation&lt;/code> (schedule::OperationOp)&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>&lt;em>An operation to schedule.&lt;/em>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Syntax:&lt;/p>
